[7.041939, "o", "  \u2705 Report saved: iot_executive_report_20260327.md\r\n\r\n======================================================================\r\n\u2728 ORCHESTRATION COMPLETE\r\n======================================================================\r\n\r\n\ud83d\udcca Results:\r\n   \u2022 3 Executive Reports Generated\r\n   \u2022 12 SQL Queries Executed\r\n   \u2022 6 AI Analysis Sessions\r\n   \u2022 100% Quality Validation\r\n\r\n\u23f1\ufe0f  Total Time: 18 seconds\r\n\ud83d\udcc1 Reports saved to: ./crewai_reports/\r\n\r\n\ud83c\udfaf Business Value Delivered:\r\n   \u2022 Revenue optimization strategies\r\n   \u2022 Customer retention insights\r\n"]
